,'2017-12-18 16:13:11',0,1),(86,'阿萨德',3,'201712/image/efcf4e65-ccdf-440e-9c16-5fcac4a9dc14.jpg','<p>3333333333333333333333333333333333333333333333333333333333二位无无无无无从666666666668888888888888888888888</p>','2017-12-18 15:53:00',NULL,0,'2017-12-18 15:53:08',23,0),(87,'不错',1,'201712/image/8c1b7a04-9362-47c2-a353-dadeed1e6ebc.jpg','<p>挺好哒1234569090</p>','2017-12-18 16:13:44',NULL,1,'2017-12-20 17:42:57',0,0),(88,'王毅会见印度外长:2017年中印关系并不令人满意',1,'201712/image/a90e4704-410a-4f01-8531-13113e705efd.png','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/committeewb/ueditor/20171219/image/1513669402775083883.jpeg\" title=\"1513669402775083883.jpeg\" alt=\"u=2118226970,2697914336&amp;fm=173&amp;s=E6E0D54E9EEAC4DE82257DBE03005010&amp;w=550&amp;h=428&amp;img.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">12月11日，外交部长王毅在新德里出席中俄印外长第十五次会晤期间会见印度外长斯瓦拉吉。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">王毅表示，2017年中印关系总体保持发展势头，双方都为此做出了努力，但并不令人满意。印度边防部队越界造成的洞朗事件使双边关系经受严重考验。此事最终通过外交手段予以和平解决，体现了双边关系日趋成熟，但教训值得汲取，应避免再次发生。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中印是两大文明古国和新兴市场国家，都肩负发展和振兴的历史使命，对世界大势和国际事务有着相同或相近看法，理应成为天然的合作伙伴。两国领导人曾指出，中印双方应视对方为机遇而不是挑战，是伙伴而不是对手。双方要切实将这些重要判断落到实处，形成更广泛的共识，变成更具体的举措，不断扩大双边关系的积极面，不断积累两国交往的正能量。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">王毅表示，中印关系正处于一个关键时期，两国之间最重要的还是要真正培育起相互信任。有了互信，具体问题就有望在互谅互让基础上予以解决，缺乏互信，个别问题就会不断发酵溢出，侵蚀双边关系大局。为此，双方要加强各层级战略沟通，恢复已建立的对话机制，深化各领域务实合作，同时管控好存在的分歧，维护好边界地区的和平安宁。“中印用一个声音说话，世界都会聆听”。希望这一天能够早日到来。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">斯瓦拉吉表示，印度始终高度重视对华关系，将其作为印度外交政策的重要组成部分。作为两大发展中国家，印中关系的意义超越双边范畴，对地区乃至世界均具有重要影响。在当前世界形势复杂多变的背景下，印中关系虽遇到一些挑战，但总体保持平稳发展，两国通过外交手段解决洞朗事件，充分体现了双方的政治智慧。印方始终认为，印中之间的共同点远远大于分歧，两国应加强战略沟通，增进战略互信，绝不能让分歧演变成争端，争端演变成冲突。印方愿与中方恢复各项双边机制性安排，推进各领域合作。同时管控好分歧，共同维护边界地区的和平安宁。只有印中携起手来，亚洲世纪才会真正到来。</p><p><br/></p>','2017-12-19 15:42:49',NULL,0,'2017-12-19 15:46:30',4,1),(89,'张一山',1,'','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\">张一山，著名童星，凭借在《小兵张嘎》中的佟乐一角出道，后参演《家有儿女》饰演刘星而爆红，最近凭借在《余罪》中的出彩表现人气达到顶峰，但是张一山的父母是谁，家庭背景究竟怎么样，外界一直知之甚少。张一山是何许人也?为何能取得这样的成就。</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://img1.ynet.com/2017/12/22/f9f075d5616b95cefb4c6eccbe3bb8f7.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\">自从张一山出道乃至成名以来，张一山的父母一直非常低调，没有张一山父母的任何报道。看完张一山个人资料及其父母背景，大家便都明白了。<br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://img2.ynet.com/2017/12/22/07558b02c1a0c21883b00a9bbca6f2de.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\">韩红在一次公益活动中暴露一个“惊天”的秘密，称张一山是她的侄子，“从小到大没公布过，拍《家有儿女》时，我和他爸妈几乎没管过他，是自由生长。我很欣慰这个孩子很有爱心，对老人很孝顺。”韩红表示，以前没提过张一山不是因为他没名，而是不希望他在光环下成长。现在把他带出来做公益活动是因为他有粉丝量，可以一起做慈善了，“我希望他长大了成为一个艺术家，像李雪健老师那样。而不是小星星，星星虽耀眼转瞬即逝 但是慈悲可以常驻人间。”<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://img1.ynet.com/2017/12/22/2ec2f3ebcf63ff6a6892231d092842bc.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\">外界一直盛传张一山家庭背景显赫，但都未获当事人任何正面回应。据说，张一山的父亲叫张晓武，就是张一山现在的经纪人，父子俩时常一起练武，一起打篮球，感情很好，张爸爸的背景并没有传闻中的那么显赫，他曾经是一名普通的话剧演员。在张一山的成长道路上，张爸爸起到了重要的作用。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://img3.ynet.com/2017/12/22/70b837bdf6c0a3552b8fedfde229d61e.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\">为了让儿子安心工作不受影响，张一山的父母非常低调，很早就决定不接受任何媒体采访，这也就是关于张一山父母资料很少的原因。有传闻说张一山的母亲叫刘希风，据说张一山在拍摄《家有儿女》过程中张妈妈便全程陪同，为了儿子的演绎事业，张妈妈甚至放弃了工作，可见对儿子爱的深沉。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\">一路走来，有些人说张一山运气好一点，有人说他有韩红这个姑姑撑腰。其实，张一山自身的努力和进步都是被观众看在眼里的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://img3.ynet.com/2017/12/22/16ca5dc8d4810c06a71ca18291e5771d.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\">对于当红的“小鲜肉”现象，张一山说“一个明星不一定是好演员，一个好演员也不一定会成为明星”。他并不追求变成多红的明星，相反，他还是会认认真真的演戏，努力做个观众口中的好演员。</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/committeewb/ueditor/20171222/image/1513922906736095321.png\" title=\"1513922906736095321.png\" alt=\"索隆.png\" width=\"473\" height=\"349\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p>','2017-12-19 15:48:05',NULL,0,'2017-12-20 09:03:21',14,1),(92,'678',1,'','<p>d<br/></p>','2017-12-19 16:16:24',NULL,1,'2017-12-20 17:43:00',0,0),(93,'水电费方法方法付付付付付',3,'','<p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://20.14.3.35:8080/committeewb/admin/media/js/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_jpg.gif\"/><a style=\"font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;\" href=\"/committeewb/ueditor/20171219/attachment/1513671567919061253.png\" title=\"印章2 拷贝.png\">印章2 拷贝.png</a></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">sdfsdf的滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴<br/></p>','2017-12-19 16:17:32',NULL,0,'2017-12-19 16:17:58',0,1),(95,'升 萨达 撒地方',8,'201712/image/9ca4fd7b-0357-4375-a810-d14f78da49d1.jpg','<p>2017-12-20&nbsp;10:31:29</p>','2017-12-20 10:31:07',NULL,1,'2017-12-20 17:43:06',0,0),(96,'Python网页爬虫&文本处理&科学计算&机器学习&数据挖掘兵器谱',8,'201712/image/ed38b5c5-18f5-4315-8762-a355903cefb7.jpg','<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">转载自“我爱自然语言处理”：<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.52nlp.cn\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"invisible\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; font-family: a; color: transparent; text-shadow: none; background-color: transparent;\">http://www.</span><span class=\"visible\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">52nlp.cn</span><span class=\"invisible\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; font-family: a; color: transparent; text-shadow: none; background-color: transparent;\"></span><span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a>，已获得授权。更多内容可见公众号：“牛衣古柳”（ID：Deserts-X）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">周末时看到这篇不错的文章，其中介绍了诸多python第三方库和工具，与大家分享下，也算是门可罗雀的本号第一次转载文章。后续看到精彩的文章也会继续分享。</p><p><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-59672d75dd11bcc5ba832741fd0ba009_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"700\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Image Photograph by Pavliha Getty</p><hr/><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">曾经因为<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//www.52nlp.cn/%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%258D%2590%25EF%25BC%258D%25E7%2594%25A8python%25E8%25BF%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2584%25B6%25E8%25AF%25AD%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%25A4%2584%25E7%2590%2586%25EF%25BC%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%25AF%2591-nltk%25E9%2585%258D%25E5%25A5%2597%25E4%25B9%25A6\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">NLTK<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a>的缘故开始学习Python，之后渐渐成为我工作中的第一辅助脚本语言，虽然开发语言是C/C++，但平时的很多文本数据处理任务都交给了Python。离开腾讯创业后，第一个作品<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//coursegraph.com/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">课程图谱<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a>也是选择了Python系的Flask框架，渐渐的将自己的绝大部分工作交给了Python。这些年来，接触和使用了很多Python工具包，特别是在文本处理，科学计算，机器学习和数据挖掘领域，有很多很多优秀的Python工具包可供使用，所以作为Pythoner，也是相当幸福的。其实如果仔细留意微博，你会发现很多这方面的分享，自己也Google了一下，发现也有同学总结了“<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//qxde01.blog.163.com/blog/static/67335744201368101922991/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">Python机器学习库<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a>”，不过总感觉缺少点什么。最近流行一个词，全栈工程师（full stack engineer），作为一个苦逼的创业者，天然的要把自己打造成一个full stack engineer，而这个过程中，这些Python工具包给自己提供了足够的火力，所以想起了这个系列。当然，这也仅仅是抛砖引玉，希望大家能提供更多的线索，来汇总整理一套Python网页爬虫，文本处理，科学计算，机器学习和数据挖掘的兵器谱。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">一、Python网页爬虫工具集</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一个真实的项目，一定是从获取数据开始的。无论文本处理，机器学习和数据挖掘，都需要数据，除了通过一些渠道购买或者下载的专业数据外，常常需要大家自己动手爬数据，这个时候，爬虫就显得格外重要了，幸好，Python提供了一批很不错的网页爬虫工具框架，既能爬取数据，也能获取和清洗数据，我们也就从这里开始了：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//scrapy.org/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">Scrapy<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Scrapy, a fast high-level screen scraping and web crawling framework for Python.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">鼎鼎大名的Scrapy，相信不少同学都有耳闻，<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//coursegraph.com/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">课程图谱<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a>中的很多课程都是依靠Scrapy抓去的，这方面的介绍文章有很多，推荐大牛pluskid早年的一篇文章：《<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//blog.pluskid.org/%3Fp%3D366\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">Scrapy 轻松定制网络爬虫<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a>》，历久弥新。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">官方主页：<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//scrapy.org/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">http://scrapy.org/<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Github代码页:<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttps%3A//github.com/scrapy/scrapy\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">https://github.com/scrapy/scrapy<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">Beautiful Soup<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">You didn’t write that awful page. You’re just trying to get some data out of it. Beautiful Soup is here to help. Since 2004, it’s been saving programmers hours or days of work on quick-turnaround screen scraping projects.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">读书的时候通过《集体智慧编程》这本书知道Beautiful Soup的，后来也偶尔会用用，非常棒的一套工具。客观的说，Beautifu Soup不完全是一套爬虫工具，需要配合urllib使用，而是一套HTML/XML数据分析，清洗和获取工具。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">官方主页：<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">http://www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttps%3A//github.com/grangier/python-goose\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">Python-Goose<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Html Content / Article Extractor, web scrapping lib in Python</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttps%3A//github.com/GravityLabs/goose\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">Goose<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a>最早是用Java写得，后来用Scala重写，是一个Scala项目。Python-Goose用Python重写，依赖了Beautiful Soup。前段时间用过，感觉很不错，给定一个文章的URL, 获取文章的标题和内容很方便。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Github主页：<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttps%3A//github.com/grangier/python-goose\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">https://github.com/grangier/python-goose<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">二、Python文本处理工具集</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从网页上获取文本数据之后，依据任务的不同，就需要进行基本的文本处理了，譬如对于英文来说，需要基本的tokenize，对于中文，则需要常见的中文分词，进一步的话，无论英文中文，还可以词性标注，句法分析，关键词提取，文本分类，情感分析等等。这个方面，特别是面向英文领域，有很多优秀的工具包，我们一一道来。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//www.nltk.org/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">NLTK<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a>— Natural Language Toolkit</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">NLTK is a leading platform for building Python programs to work with human language data. It provides easy-to-use interfaces to over 50 corpora and lexical resources such as WordNet, along with a suite of text processing libraries for classification, tokenization, stemming, tagging, parsing, and semantic reasoning, and an active discussion forum.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">搞自然语言处理的同学应该没有人不知道NLTK吧，这里也就不多说了。不过推荐两本书籍给刚刚接触NLTK或者需要详细了解NLTK的同学: 一个是官方的《Natural Language Processing with Python》，以介绍NLTK里的功能用法为主，同时附带一些Python知识，同时国内陈涛同学友情翻译了一个中文版，这里可以看到：<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//www.52nlp.cn/%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%258D%2590%25EF%25BC%258D%25E7%2594%25A8python%25E8%25BF%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2584%25B6%25E8%25AF%25AD%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%25A4%2584%25E7%2590%2586%25EF%25BC%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%25AF%2591-nltk%25E9%2585%258D%25E5%25A5%2597%25E4%25B9%25A6\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">推荐《用Python进行自然语言处理》中文翻译-NLTK配套书<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a>；另外一本是《Python Text Processing with NLTK 2.0 Cookbook》，这本书要深入一些，会涉及到NLTK的代码结构，同时会介绍如何定制自己的语料和模型等，相当不错。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">官方主页：<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//www.nltk.org/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">http://www.nltk.org/<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Github代码页：<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttps%3A//github.com/nltk/nltk\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">https://github.com/nltk/nltk<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//www.clips.ua.ac.be/pattern\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">Pattern<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Pattern is a web mining module for the Python programming language.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">It has tools for data mining (Google, Twitter and Wikipedia API, a web crawler, a HTML DOM parser), natural language processing (part-of-speech taggers, n-gram search, sentiment analysis, WordNet), machine learning (vector space model, clustering, SVM), network analysis and canvas visualization.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Pattern由比利时安特卫普大学CLiPS实验室出品，客观的说，Pattern不仅仅是一套文本处理工具，它更是一套web数据挖掘工具，囊括了数据抓取模块（包括Google, Twitter, 维基百科的API，以及爬虫和HTML分析器），文本处理模块（词性标注，情感分析等），机器学习模块(VSM, 聚类，SVM）以及可视化模块等，可以说，Pattern的这一整套逻辑也是这篇文章的组织逻辑，不过这里我们暂且把Pattern放到文本处理部分。我个人主要使用的是它的英文处理模块<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//www.clips.ua.ac.be/pages/pattern-en\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">Pattern.en<span class=\"icon-external\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 24px; speak: none; font-feature-settings: normal; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: icomoon !important;\"></span></a>, 有很多很不错的文本处理功能，包括基础的tokenize, 词性标注，句子切分，语法检查，拼写纠错，情感分析，句法分析等，相当不错。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">官方主页：<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//link.jianshu.com/%3Ft%3Dhttp%3A//www.clips.ua.ac.be/pattern\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(64, 64, 64, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer;\">http://www.clips.ua.ac.be/pattern</a></p>','2017-12-20 13:53:33',NULL,1,'2017-12-20 17:43:07',0,0),(97,'8909',1,'','<p><img src=\"http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0059.gif\"/></p>','2017-12-21 13:46:47',NULL,1,NULL,0,0),(99,'蜀南青语',5,'201712/image/371a3405-02bc-4e48-9d97-4961d61b6c0c.png','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, 宋体, sans-serif, tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>12月14日消息，据国外媒体报道，从乔布斯生前就开始规划、历时7年、主体已经建成、即将投入使用的苹果新总部，造价高达50亿美元，是目前美国造价最高的建筑，比世界贸易中心一号楼还要贵。</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, 宋体, sans-serif, tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><span class=\"img-turn-left\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\"><em class=\"i-turn-zuo mr-5\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 11px; height: 11px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: -610px -272px; background-image: url(&quot;https://iknowpc.bdimg.com/static/question/pkg/aio_z.ef54f77.png&quot;);\"></em>向左转</span><span class=\"f-pipe\" style=\"color: rgb(232, 236, 238); margin: 0px 8p